  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "Summary\nYoroi DRep votes YES on \"Rare Evo and Dev Gov Day 2026: Cardano Title Sponsorship\" as a practical investment in Cardano's ecosystem visibility and governance coordination.\n\nRationale\n• Established platform with a track record.\nRare Evo has consistently delivered well-organised events that bring the Cardano community together at scale. Supporting a known entity with demonstrated execution capacity is a lower-risk use of treasury funds than backing an unproven initiative of comparable cost.\n• Governance Day adds substance beyond sponsorship.\nRare Dev Gov Day provides dedicated space for governance discussion and developer coordination that complements the broader event. For Yoroi, this is a meaningful part of the value proposition, not an afterthought.\n\nConclusion\nRare Evo is an established platform and the scope of this sponsorship is well-defined. Yoroi believes this is a sound use of treasury resources for ecosystem presence and community coordination."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}